snippet.title: Subluminal Pre-Alpha Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1594110/Subluminal/

Subluminal is a 3D driving platformer about gaining speed and driving fast.  

Vehicles have precise maneuverability allowing you to jump in the air and manipulate your orientation to drive on all surfaces.

All vehicles are equipped with a space displacing mechanism known in Subluminal as boost to propel the vehicle forward.  This not only allows you to gain speed, but provides aerodynamic control.
